Load the plugin with a clone.

  $ antigen-bundle $PLUGIN_DIR &> /dev/null
  $ ls $ANTIGEN_BUNDLES
  cram-testdir-* (glob)

Empty the record.

  $ _ANTIGEN_BUNDLE_RECORD=()
  $ antigen list
  You don't have any bundles.
