Load the plugin again with no local clone.

  $ antigen-bundle $PLUGIN_DIR --no-local-clone
  $ antigen list
  cram-testdir-*/test-plugin @ master (glob)
  $ ls $ANTIGEN_BUNDLES
  cram-testdir-* (glob)

